{"title":"亚洲的太阳——为第十一届亚运会作","authors":["沈洪胜"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":8,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚洲的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为第十一届亚运会作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈洪胜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一改过去憔悴的面容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你跃然空中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向全世界热情地微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一种证明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回忆爷爷的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖父已经死了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的子孙也不再"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛着烟枪上炕头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚洲重又浮现太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个世纪后终于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醒了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚洲的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血仍然是红的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骨头仍然是硬的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皮肤仍然是黄的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推开窗户"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说亚洲的太阳永远枯黄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看　一支支雄鹰从这里腾飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个骄傲在这里诞生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如蓝眼睛不相信的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回首总是曲折的慨叹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要感激那洋炮的轰击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"治愈了祖父遗传的病"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚洲的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛然挥去那顶屈辱的缨帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天的巨人已不是神话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚洲的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向朋友微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界的兄弟为你鼓掌"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}